Class Tup4f

    ITup4fR, ITup4fW, ITup4R, ITupfR, ITupfW, ITupR

    public class Tup4f
extends Tupf
implements ITup4fR, ITup4fW
    This class is a simple implementation of a 4-dimensional float tuple.
